---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="POS Systems for Maine Dispensaries | Maine Dispensary Guide" description="Compare the best point-of-sale systems for Maine cannabis dispensaries. Features, pricing, compliance, and seed-to-sale integration.">
  <article>
    <header>
      <h1>POS Systems for Dispensaries</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Choosing the right point-of-sale system for your Maine cannabis dispensary</p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>Why Cannabis-Specific POS Matters</h2>
      <p>General retail POS systems won't work for cannabis dispensaries. You need specialized software that handles seed-to-sale tracking, compliance reporting, and cannabis-specific regulations.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Key Features Required</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Seed-to-Sale Tracking</strong> - Integration with state tracking system</li>
        <li><strong>Age Verification</strong> - Built-in ID scanning</li>
        <li><strong>Inventory Management</strong> - Real-time stock tracking</li>
        <li><strong>Compliance Reporting</strong> - Automatic regulatory reports</li>
        <li><strong>Tax Calculation</strong> - Maine cannabis taxes</li>
        <li><strong>Employee Management</strong> - Permissions and tracking</li>
        <li><strong>Customer Loyalty</strong> - CRM features</li>
        <li><strong>Reporting & Analytics</strong> - Sales insights</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Top POS Providers</h2>
      
      <h3>BioTrackTHC</h3>
      <p>Industry leader with comprehensive features. Used by many Maine operators.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Strengths: Robust compliance, widely adopted</li>
        <li>Price: Moderate to premium</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>MJ Freeway / Akerna</h3>
      <p>Established player with strong inventory management.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Strengths: Comprehensive reporting</li>
        <li>Price: Premium</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Leaf Logix</h3>
      <p>Modern, user-friendly interface with good customer support.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Strengths: Ease of use, good support</li>
        <li>Price: Competitive</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Clover</h3>
      <p>Consumer-friendly with good integration options.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Strengths: Intuitive interface</li>
        <li>Price: Moderate</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Square for Retail</h3>
      <p>Simple option, may require additional compliance integration.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Strengths: Low cost, easy setup</li>
        <li>Caveat: May need add-ons for full compliance</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Maine Compliance Requirements</h2>
      <p>Your POS must integrate with Maine's seed-to-sale tracking system. Ensure your chosen system:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Integrates with Maine OCP reporting requirements</li>
        <li>Tracks all products from seed to sale</li>
        <li>Generates required compliance reports</li>
        <li>Handles Maine-specific tax calculations</li>
        <li>Maintains accurate inventory records</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Pricing Comparison</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Provider</th><th>Setup Fee</th><th>Monthly</th><th>Per Transaction</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>BioTrackTHC</td><td>$5,000+</td><td>$400-800</td><td>1-3%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>MJ Freeway</td><td>$3,000+</td><td>$300-600</td><td>1-2%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Leaf Logix</td><td>$1,500+</td><td>$200-400</td><td>1-2%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Clover</td><td>$0-500</td><td>$100-250</td><td>1.5-2.5%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Square</td><td>$0</td><td>$0-60</td><td>1.5%</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Implementation Tips</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Start the selection process early (before build-out)</li>
        <li>Request demos from multiple vendors</li>
        <li>Check references from other Maine operators</li>
        <li>Ensure 24/7 support availability</li>
        <li>Plan for training time</li>
        <li>Test thoroughly before going live</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Key Takeaways</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Cannabis-specific POS is required in Maine</li>
        <li>Seed-to-sale integration is mandatory</li>
        <li>Prices range from $5K setup + $100/mo to premium options</li>
        <li>Consider ease of use alongside features</li>
        <li>Ensure Maine compliance before choosing</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="disclaimer">
      <p><em>Pricing and features are subject to change. Verify current information with providers.</em></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  header { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2 { margin-top: 0; }
  section h3 { margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary); }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0; }
  th, td { padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  th { background: var(--color-background); }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .disclaimer { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; }
</style>
